fix(deps): Update dev dependencies and Node.js (#495)

* npx npm-check-updates -u

* npm i

* upgrade node from v14.16.1 to v14.18.1
... to fix `Not compatible with your version of node/npm: @typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin@5.1.0`

* fix `"prettier/@typescript-eslint" has been merged into "prettier"`

* npm run lint:fix

* fix `This number literal will lose precision at runtime  @typescript-eslint/no-loss-of-precision`

* disable eslint error `Parsing error: Deleting local variable in strict mode  prettier/prettier`

* npm run lint:format

* fix `SyntaxError: 'CallExpression' is not allowed in JSON.` and other prettier errors => everything is formatted correctly

* try to fix `The play() request was interrupted by a call to pause(). https://goo.gl/LdLk22`
- cf https://github.com/openwhyd/openwhyd/runs/3988567033?check_suite_focus=true#step:7:124
- cf https://github.com/openwhyd/openwhyd/runs/3988567033?check_suite_focus=true#step:7:242

* add TODOs on cy.wait() calls
